  [Octavio Vial; Martín Cuburu, Urquiola, Crespo]
Moctezuma 1 Atlante 2
  [Honorio Arteaga; José "Chanclas" Zamudio, José Gutiérrez]
Bye: Asturias, Necaxa

Week 5
[Aug 18]
Asturias 5 Moctezuma 0
  ["Charro" Argüelles (2), Enrique Larriñaga, Frade, Solar (og)]
Necaxa 3 América 0
  [Méndez (2), Vicente García]
Bye: Atlante, España, Marte, Selección Jalisco

Week 6
[Aug 25]
